overview: The producers of Hustle Up video magazine showcase the Latino sound with a collection of exclusive music videos and candid interviews with some of the biggest stars in hip-hop. Featured artists include Don Omar, Hector "El Father," Ivy Queen, Luny Tunes, the Mas Flow Family, Bimbo and Zion y Lennox -- plus exclusive behind-the-scenes footage captured at the Mix 107.7 Mix Action Sports concert in Puerto Rico.
title: Hustle Up Latino
